metadata.name: Through the Looking-Glass
metadata.description:
Moscow, Russia. May 6th 2012.

A policeman looks at protesters during "March of Millions" mass protest rally. The day before Vladimir Putin's inauguration.

From ''Ground Control'' photo series dedicated to mass protest activity in Russia (2010-2018).

Awards:

- «Kolga Tbilisi Photo 2019» / shortlist.
- «Lensculture Black & White Photography Awards 2018» /  2nd place single.
- “PDN Photo Annual 2013” / winner in nomination “Student Work”.
- “Photomania 2013” / Balfc Biennale of Photography) / Gran-Prix.
- “Best of Russia 2012” / Gran-Prix.
